               <person>
                  <persName role="owner" corresp="PRS0000">The name of the original donor, ʾAʾzanä Krǝstos,has been erased from the headings of the Gospels, fully or partly, but has been preserved on fol. 106ra. On fol. 19r "his assistant" (rädǝʾu) is mentioned, the first part of the name being Wäldä. &#xD;
